name: steamed egg with minced
ingredients:
- eggs: 4
- minced pork: 200g
- prawns, optional: 50g
steps:
- put the kettle on
- mince meat and prawns
- season mince and place in bowl to be steamed
- place bowl in steamer and steam for 5 minutes
- in the mean time, crack eggs and add 1.5 times the amount of water. season and mix well
- add eggy water to mince and steam over medium heat for 15 minutes
